      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 You\u2019ve got to see this beauty \u2013 it\u2019s honestly like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and it still has that brand-new feel inside and out. No scratches, no dents, just pure perfection! It drives like an absolute dream, and I\u2019m so excited for it to find a new home where it\u2019ll be loved just as much as I\u2019ve loved it. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
