    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a museum-grade 1994 Mazda RX-7 FD, preserved in its original factory configuration. This specimen features the iconic 13B-REW sequential twin-turbocharged rotary engine, delivering seamless boost transition through the factory vacuum-actuated control system. The chassis retains its legendary 50:50 weight distribution, paired with a pristine four-wheel double-wishbone suspension and a Torsen limited-slip differential for surgical cornering precision. Every component, from the uncracked dash to the original five-speed short-throw shifter, reflects meticulous ownership. The compression remains within factory specifications, and the cooling system has been rigorously maintained to ensure thermal efficiency. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a zero-modification, collector-standard Japanese icon with perfect mechanical synchronization.",
      "price": 48750.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
