    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional vehicle that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. This car has been meticulously maintained, garage-kept under a breathable cover, and driven only in fair weather. The exterior paint retains its deep, mirror-like luster without a single swirl mark, scratch, or stone chip. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary of luxury; the premium leather seats are supple and free of any creases or wear, still carrying that distinct new-car scent. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity surround sound system to the advanced dual-zone climate control, functions flawlessly. Under the hood, the engine bay is spotless, reflecting a rigorous maintenance schedule performed exclusively by factory-certified technicians. With extremely low mileage and a comprehensive service history available for review, this is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle in peerless condition. No dents, no odors, no excuses\u2014just pure automotive excellence for the discerning collector.",
