      "description": "Hey there! I am so excited to show you this absolute gem. Honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one\u2014it's in truly pristine condition, both inside and out. It drives like a dream and has been kept in a climate-controlled garage. You won't find a cleaner ride out there! I'm sad to see it go, but I\u2019d love for it to find a home where it\u2019ll be just as loved. Feel free to reach out with any questions! \u2728\ud83d\ude97",
